== 製作 ==
*2013年12月12日，製片方[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]初步宣布由[[英國|英國]]導演[[喬·萊特|喬·萊特]]執導此片，上映日為2015年6月26日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=112440 |title=Warner Bros. Sets Joe Wright's Pan for June 26, 2015 |access-date=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205050847/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=112440 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年1月17日，華納兄弟將上映日移至2015年7月17日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=113669 |title=Warner Bros. Pictures Pushes Batman vs. Superman Back to 2016 |access-date=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006072251/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=113669 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*2014年1月24日，確定由[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]飾演[[黑鬍子|黑鬍子]]一角<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/24/hugh-jackman-peter-pan-blackbeard/ |title=Hugh Jackman signs on for Joe Wright's Peter Pan movie |access-date=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2015-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111100609/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/24/hugh-jackman-peter-pan-blackbeard/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[鲁妮·玛拉|鲁妮·玛拉]]飾演{{link-en|莉莉·虎蓮|Tiger Lily (Peter Pan)}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/tiger-lilly-warner-bros-pan-1201102262/ |title=Rooney Mara to Play Tiger Lily in Warner Bros.' 'Pan' |access-date=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119174937/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/tiger-lilly-warner-bros-pan-1201102262/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主角則是起用新人[[萊維·米勒|萊維·米勒]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/levi-miller-tapped-to-play-peter-pan-in-warner-bros-pan-exclusive-1201136941/ |title=Levi Miller Tapped to Play Peter Pan in Warner Bros.' 'Pan' |access-date=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2017-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212084147/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/levi-miller-tapped-to-play-peter-pan-in-warner-bros-pan-exclusive-1201136941/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年4月，[[阿曼達·西耶弗里德|阿曼達·西耶弗里德]]加入劇組。
