== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度27%，基於171條評論，平均分為4.6/10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pan_2015/|title=Pan (2015)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-10-11|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126032920/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pan_2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分36，代表「普遍不佳」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pan|title=Pan reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2015-10-11|archive-date=2018-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804033742/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pan|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分5.8，差評居多。

=== 票房 ===
美國首周票房僅1531萬美元，排於《[[絕地救援|絕地救援]]》（3700萬美元）和《[[尖叫旅社2|尖叫旅社2]]》（2040萬美元）之後<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/martian-pan-the-walk-weekend-box-office-1201572119/ |title=‘Martian’ Still Frying ‘Pan’ At The Weekend B.O.; ‘Steve Jobs’ Posting Best Theater Average This Year – Late Night Update |work=deadline.com |access-date=2015-10-13 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2015%2F10%2Fmartian-pan-the-walk-weekend-box-office-1201572119%2F&date=2016-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，票房略低。

